{"tid":2074633,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【天譴】中國官媒警告！ 重慶綦江8小時內將出現1940年來最大洪水","createTime":"2020-06-22T08:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T13:31:09.000Z","uid":293677,"like":150,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"55dfd83f61d95e390484f3d8ccdde3221f49d704","tid":2074633,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:57:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3205505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3205505&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F7eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=a2a0682d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3205505&h=f2823812\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3205505</a><br />\n<br />\n2020-06-22 15:37:04<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國近期暴雨成災，高達24省遭到洪災侵襲，今日下午中國官媒《央視》急在微博上表示受暴雨和上游溪水暴漲影響，重慶綦江流域已超過防洪限制水位1公尺，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">預計在未來8小時內綦江流域將出現1940年來最大的洪水</span></span>，官方表示已緊急疏散4萬人。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，重慶市水文監測總站在今日上午11時50分發布洪水紅色預警，表示受強降雨和上游溪水暴漲影響，綦江流域重慶段全線在<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未來8小時內將出現「超歷史洪水」，此次紅色預警是重慶市水文監測總站1940年建站以來首次發布。</span></span>預計江津區綦江五岔站最高水位將超過防洪限制水位5.7～6.3公尺左右，漲幅可達10至11公尺左右。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不少重慶網友表示不到中午，許多地區都嚴重淹水，濱江路也淹一層樓高，</span></span>現在水位仍持續上漲，官方表示已緊急疏散4萬民眾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/06/22/phpjihScu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F06%2F22%2FphpjihScu.jpg&h=bc1486fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/06/22/phpvnMtZt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F06%2F22%2FphpvnMtZt.jpg&h=f2433d7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vwb19eP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvwb19eP.jpg&h=7a2dce63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hoov2zU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHoov2zU.png&h=2b5cd74f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔好俾佢停<br />\n<br />\n天譴係會繼續黎</span>"},{"pid":"ca00aaed3416afc7188ee0ffb40530ed45d7c3ed","tid":2074633,"uid":34047,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:05:22.000Z","msg":"變水城景點<br />\n可以同威尼斯鬥過"},{"pid":"954f837976d76dca0ca225ea00c1a53fcc9ba8ac","tid":2074633,"uid":180293,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:20:22.000Z","msg":"唔爛邊有得起<br />\nGDP GOGOGO"},{"pid":"8c9ccc27c37b0ff4c71c617fb15f7276a3a08b2b","tid":2074633,"uid":193295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:21:07.000Z","msg":"正啊<br />\n死多D蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7244a4e2c9e0dada826b8dcb72660cb2602d6c43","tid":2074633,"uid":209248,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:21:25.000Z","msg":"清洗大地"},{"pid":"aaee11742d380a51d291c53c42724fd7af70f045","tid":2074633,"uid":180173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:21:33.000Z","msg":"小小野點會難到我地既偉大黨，信政府，唔怕！"},{"pid":"0db89e0bb2e7d14fdabe89b9ec9eb779e09b07c0","tid":2074633,"uid":318025,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ca00aaed3416afc7188ee0ffb40530ed45d7c3ed","tid":2074633,"uid":34047,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:05:22.000Z","msg":"變水城景點<br />\n可以同威尼斯鬥過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:21:45.000Z","msg":"支那斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c73