0-06-22T11:18:35.000Z","msg":"收咗皮？"},{"pid":"b93ca93a07bb0d03a35b89359fd784883dfdc5a8","tid":2074633,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55dfd83f61d95e390484f3d8ccdde3221f49d704","tid":2074633,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:57:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3205505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3205505&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F7eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=a2a0682d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3205505&h=f2823812\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3205505</a><br />\n<br />\n2020-06-22 15:37:04<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國近期暴雨成災，高達24省遭到洪災侵襲，今日下午中國官媒《央視》急在微博上表示受暴雨和上游溪水暴漲影響，重慶綦江流域已超過防洪限制水位1公尺，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">預計在未來8小時內綦江流域將出現1940年來最大的洪水</span></span>，官方表示已緊急疏散4萬人。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，重慶市水文監測總站在今日上午11時50分發布洪水紅色預警，表示受強降雨和上游溪水暴漲影響，綦江流域重慶段全線在<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未來8小時內將出現「超歷史洪水」，此次紅色預警是重慶市水文監測總站1940年建站以來首次發布。</span></span>預計江津區綦江五岔站最高水位將超過防洪限制水位5.7～6.3公尺左右，漲幅可達10至11公尺左右。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不少重慶網友表示不到中午，許多地區都嚴重淹水，濱江路也淹一層樓高，</span></span>現在水位仍持續上漲，官方表示已緊急疏散4萬民眾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/06/22/phpjihScu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F06%2F22%2FphpjihScu.jpg&h=bc1486fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/06/22/phpvnMtZt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F06%2F22%2FphpvnMtZt.jpg&h=f2433d7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vwb19eP.